node.text:
Listed by @LivSellsMiami 🔑✨
This beautifully designed 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence at Faena House, an 18-story luxury condominium designed by Foster + Partners. 😍 Featuring 2,238 Sq Ft of indoor living, 1,190 Sq Ft of terrace with views from downtown to the Atlantic Ocean making this a true indoor / outdoor living experience. 🌊

Listed at $6,450,000 

Contact @LivSellsMiami for more information 🔑
-

Exclusive @3SAEstate listing 🔑
Top modern luxury villa in the Golf Valley asking €4,195,000 🌟

This newly built luxury villa is situated in the heart of Nueva Andalucía’s golf valley with a south orientation providing the best of views.

The villa is characterized by an elegant living space with modern clean lines and plenty of glass providing natural light and seamless integration of indoor and outdoor living. The property is everything you need to experience the best of the Mediterranean lifestyle, distributed on three levels.

📍 #Marbella

✔️ Surface 517 M²⁠⠀⁠
✔️ Plot 1258 M²⠀
✔️ Terrace 360 M²
✔️ ⁠5 Bedrooms⁠⠀
✔️ Large roof terrace

✔️ Outdoor gym
✔️ Jacuzzi
